# Whitelist build context: ignore everything by default, then re-include
# only the files docker/score/Dockerfile actually COPYs. Self-maintaining
# — new files added anywhere in the repo are excluded automatically.
# Only update this file when the Dockerfile starts reading a new path.

**

# Files COPYed by docker/score/Dockerfile (anything Dockerfile needs to see).
!registry.yaml
!docker/score/Dockerfile
!docker/score/inject
!docker/score/inject/anc
!docker/score/install-tools.sh
!docker/score/score-anc100.sh
